{
  "stem": "7358.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could open a window and run out to the main street, while the people that lived in back of us could only leave by the gate, what was manned by-- by Ukrainians and Germans.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did you ever leave that way?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I used to run out on occasions, to-- to get some food from-- from-- from people that-- from-- that we used to know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to pay them whatever little bit we had, you know, just whatever money we had, or jewelry, or whatever we-- we could exchange for food.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other people could not do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were always frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, every time-- if you were caught, you were killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no hesitation of killing anybody that broke the rules.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The reason they did that is because the regular population-- the-- the Germans were very great on issuing identification cards constantly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they always needed photographs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the-- the-- the non-Jewish population had to come to our place of business to take the pictures.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for their convenience, they left us and some other professional people-- some-- some tailors and shoemakers and other professionals that the general public needed their services.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let them live on the front street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they all could sort of have the access to the main street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my mother and my father used to work in the photography place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from time to time, when there wasn't too much work to do, my father used to go on-- go also to work on the road construction.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What did you do during that time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a-- I-- I used to-- we-- I used to break up big stones into pebbles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my job.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
